In your NODE.js PowerShell Terminal:

npm update nvm
nvm install 8.1.2
alias new nvm version
$ nvm alias default 8.1.2
npm update npm
npm i -g npm
install Firebase CLI

$ npm install -g firebase-tools

create a subdirectory

$ mkdir my-project-name
cd into new subdirectory

Create project in Firebase console

credential Firebase
$ firebase login -no-localhost

initialize Firebase
$ firebase init

run devserver
$ firebase serve --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8080
